{"tid":807124,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一個] 煩膠同事嘅膠事","createTime":"2018-09-05T09:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T09:32:28.000Z","uid":206675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac81c29fa3fe95265cbe11f7029aaa6369aa1f6b","tid":807124,"uid":206675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"先拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同事係個40幾歲嘅大叔嚟，唔知係咪缺乏家庭溫暖，成日都係公司R水吹，不論清潔啊姐定我呢啲後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，有次清潔啊姐傾起屋企嘢，啊姐話自己個仔30幾歲都未有女朋友，覺得好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後個煩膠同事居然問哂全公司啲女同事想唔想識男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就係其中一位受害人，我話我有男朋友，佢話男未婚女未嫁，試下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係比佢吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲有好撚多膠事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}